node.text: You know @antoni from @netflix's @queereye, but now now it's time to meet his rescue pup @neonthemutt! 🐶 Neon was emaciated and losing so much fur when Antoni brought her home from @austinpetsalive to foster her, but he quickly fell in love and had to adopt her. Now Neon and Antoni are inseparable 💛

node.title: You Know Me...Now Meet My Pet With @antoni + @neonthemutt

Now Neon and Antoni are inseparable 💛
